'''許芯悅''' （{{lang-en|Katie Hui}}，{{bd|1990年|6月25日}}），原名許詠媚，[[大灣區|大灣區]]女藝人、演員、主持、歌手、直播主、[[淘宝网|淘寶]]買手。被[[莊思明|莊思明]]等一眾藝人批評多年間只想借媒體編造不實遙言而見報<ref>{{Citation|title=許芯悅哭訴｜楊明女友莊思明還擊：有個小丑哄自己笑|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8OnxDjNxRN4|accessdate=2022-07-01|language=zh-Hans-CN}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=黃梓恒 |date=2020-09-23 |title=許芯悅哭訴｜楊明女友莊思明還擊：有個小丑哄自己笑 |url=https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/527572/許芯悅哭訴-楊明女友莊思明還擊-有個小丑哄自己笑 |website=香港01 |language=zh-HK |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=許芯悅喊住爆遭人身攻擊 莊思明狂寸：小丑博見報 - 晴報 - 娛樂 - 娛樂 |url=https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2762116/https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2762116%2F%E8%A8%B1%E8%8A%AF%E6%82%85%E5%96%8A%E4%BD%8F%E7%88%86%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%20%E8%8E%8A%E6%80%9D%E6%98%8E%E7%8B%82%E5%AF%B8%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%91%E5%8D%9A%E8%A6%8B%E5%A0%B1 |website=skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk |language=zh |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Kwok |first=Ling |title=被指不滿許芯悅與楊明拍戲親熱發信息恐嚇女方 莊思明IG反擊：有個小丑氹自己開心 |url=https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/212412/被指不滿許芯悅與楊明拍戲親熱發信息恐嚇女方-莊思明ig反擊-有個小丑氹自己開心 |website=HK 港生活 |language=zh-hk |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref>然而卻沒有任何代表作和貢獻。近年卻被聲稱[[ViuTV|Viu tv]]前員工把對話紀錄於群組流出見證許各不實謊言及滿口穢語。及後更被在[[淘寶售賣假貨事件|淘寶]]買盒<ref>{{Cite web |title=登录 Facebook |url=https://www.facebook.com/ |website=Facebook |language=zh-Hans |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref>卻聲稱自家設計<ref>{{Cite web |title=秘の菓子𝐃𝐞́𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐞𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐭 - 秘の菓子𝐃𝐞́𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐞𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐭♥️情人節限量版禮盒🎁 ~𝕍𝕒𝕝𝕖𝕟𝕥𝕚𝕟𝕖'𝕤... |url=https://www.facebook.com/Delisecret.hk/photos/a.108370854519469/108858194470735/?type=3 |website=www.facebook.com |language=zh-Hans |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref>而被傳媒諷刺為「新一代甜品王」。早年心想憑童顏和甜美笑容拿取關注而向傳媒自封為「逆齡少女」<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://yes-news.com/51305/Stars-Girl%25E9%2580%2586%25E9%25BD%25A1%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E8%258A%25AF%25E6%2582%2585Katie|title=【Stars Girl】逆齡少女許芯悅Katie|last=|first=|date=|work=Star-HK 娛網|accessdate=2016-05-05|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202112952/http://yes-news.com/51305/Stars-Girl%E9%80%86%E9%BD%A1%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%A8%B1%E8%8A%AF%E6%82%85Katie|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾拍攝《[[怪談_(電視節目)|怪談]]》電視節目而被稱為「怪談女」，亦因事前聯繋記者拍自己在街上身穿[[比卡超|比卡超]]衣服玩全球大熱遊戲《[[精靈寶可夢GO|Pokenmon GO]]》而登上香港報紙頭版再投稿給台灣媒體自稱為「白皙童顏修圖Pokemon Go女神」。近年代表作有愛國電影「[[時代_(電影)|時代]] 」<ref>{{Cite web |title=橙新聞-OrangeNews.hk |url=https://m.orangenews.hk/details?recommendId=140377 |website=m.orangenews.hk |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref> 然而制作素質過於劣質而遭各院線一致拒絕放映。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.facebook.com/KatieHui.official/photos/a.384369595010891.1073741828.383901605057690/1022014561246388/?type=3&theater|title=【A1頭條】Pika~Pika~ PokémonGo殺到 全城捉精靈|last=|first=|date=|work=香港蘋果日報(fb)|accessdate=2016-07-26|archive-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606183459/https://www.facebook.com/KatieHui.official/photos/a.384369595010891.1073741828.383901605057690/1022014561246388/?type=3&theater|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160726/55408808|title=【A1頭條】Pika~Pika~ PokémonGo殺到 全城捉精靈|last=|first=|date=|work=香港蘋果日報|accessdate=2016-07-26|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909070131/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160726/55408808|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://beauty-twomg-yahoopartner.tumblr.com/post/148348614897/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E5%8E%BB%E5%90%A7%E7%9A%AE%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%98%E7%99%BD%E7%9A%99%E7%AB%A5%E9%A1%8Fpokemon-go%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E-%E8%A8%B1%E8%8A%AF%E6%82%85|title=【香港星正妹】去吧皮卡丘！白皙童顏Pokemon Go女神 許芯悅|last=|first=|date=|work=Yahoo奇摩名人娛樂正妹館|accessdate=02-08-2016|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201151305/https://beauty-twomg-yahoopartner.tumblr.com/post/148348614897/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E5%8E%BB%E5%90%A7%E7%9A%AE%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%98%E7%99%BD%E7%9A%99%E7%AB%A5%E9%A1%8Fpokemon-go%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E-%E8%A8%B1%E8%8A%AF%E6%